{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0176wi355EAGhA5MABGf8Bah","type":"tool_result","content":"413-- NFR1: Workflow YAML parsing and validation completes in <500ms for any valid workflow\n414-- NFR2: Agent config resolution (embedded → user → project) completes in <200ms\n415:- NFR3: Agent session spawn (fresh) completes in <5s excluding model response time\n416-- NFR4: Circuit breaker state evaluation completes in <100ms\n417-- NFR5: `codeharness status` returns in <1s regardless of run history size\n--\n427-### Integration\n428-\n429:- NFR11: Engine uses the official programmatic agent dispatch API — no direct CLI process spawning\n430-- NFR12: BMAD agent configs are read-only — engine never modifies agent YAML files\n431-- NFR13: Docker container lifecycle (start, exec, stop) is managed by the engine, not delegated to agents"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_015upEEv2DfZnR9xKiJz9ZsK","session_id":"84c2a87f-6818-4ede-b88c-dde16fd6e99b","uuid":"453e449a-d207-4344-bdd6-3d544fe3eb46","timestamp":"2026-04-02T19:29:01.125Z"}
